@startuml mgmt_plane_flow
title Management Plane Flow
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Management Plane" {
  [Azure Portal / ARM] as ARM
  [Intune] as MDM
  [Defender for Endpoint] as MDE
  [Entra ID Governance] as EIG
}
package "Policy Sources" {
  [UIAO Policy Orchestrator] as PO
  [NIST Control Mappings] as NIST
}
package "Endpoints" {
  [GCC High VMs] as VM
  [Windows Devices] as WIN
}

PO --> ARM : deploy config
NIST --> PO : control requirements
ARM --> VM : resource policy
MDM --> WIN : compliance baseline
MDE --> WIN : threat response
EIG --> ARM : identity-driven RBAC
@enduml
